    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.poster.avif?t=1681148003\" width=382 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.webm?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.mp4?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>解锁 4 个新角色加入纮的军队一起阻止妖怪的入侵。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ol><li>四个新的特殊单位：雪女、辉夜姬、清姫、花鸟卷，和她们的人物互动新能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/427d1a688e768f977d5974e92b868fe3.avif?t=1681148003\" width=596 height=359 /></span><br></li><li>一个新的支援单位：青行灯<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/5c684cd48d0ac7f9117753a2b9cb41bc.poster.avif?t=1681148003\" width=265 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/5c684cd48d0ac7f9117753a2b9cb41bc.webm?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li>四个新章节难度：休闲、普通和困难给大家挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/25285c1207382c4674e60e9de745dd7d.poster.avif?t=1681148003\" width=284 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/25285c1207382c4674e60e9de745dd7d.webm?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/25285c1207382c4674e60e9de745dd7d.mp4?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>全新的游戏模式《生存模式》，为玩家提供极致的乐趣和挑战。（需要完成3-5关卡已解锁）<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/2fc42869b165797aa91f7aa31724a4bc.avif?t=1681148003\" width=596 height=402 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>注意：</strong> 新模式仍在测试中，我们正在努力改进，直到游戏玩法稳定并且所有单位和功能都能解锁。<br></li><li>尽可能的生存吧！<br></li><li>多种新的强化和天赋构建策略。<br></li><li>具有ROGUE一样的重玩性机制。<br></li><li>高额小判奖励。<br></li><li>目前，主要支持的语言是英语和中文。其余语言将逐步更新。</li></ul></li></ol>准备好沉浸在妖怪世界中，体验此DLC带来的无尽乐趣和挑战吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/baf5799406aaec9b0bb774d3f6e8beab.poster.avif?t=1681148003\" width=600 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/baf5799406aaec9b0bb774d3f6e8beab.webm?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256730/extras/baf5799406aaec9b0bb774d3f6e8beab.mp4?t=1681148003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
